# Museum Auto Upgrader Package
This is an auto-upgrading gem script for the museum. All gems in the inventory area on the right will be deleted on script start. Transmutation to create universal gems isn't supported.
	1. Place the gems you will upgrade into your equipped area
	2. Set what your max buy level (Will not buy gems higher than that) will be in the Museum_Auto_Buyer.
	3. Set what your max craft level (Will not craft higher than that) will be in the Museum_Auto_Buyer.
	4. Press m while in the museum and let it roll. 
	
Use https://github.com/Xenos6666/TPT2_scripts/tree/modular_V2/common/execution_stack with it to save yourself hours.
